    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who apply gold to surfaces in the form of leaf, powder, or other forms to approximate the effect of solid or inlaid gold, especially as an occupation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
